React   => is a library which is used to develop UI OR frontend
        => It is developed by facebook


why?

1: very fast
2: easy event handling
3: Its small library and easy to learn
4: It manage UI by states


components :
    1: functional components
    2: class components
  


how to use react:
1:   first way:
        -> use use links in header
        {
                <script src="https://unpkg.com/react@17/umd/react.development.js" crossorigin></script>
                <script src="https://unpkg.com/react-dom@17/umd/react-dom.development.js" crossorigin></script>
                <script src="https://unpkg.com/babel-standalone@6/babel.min.js"></script>
        }

2:  second way:
        -> npx create-react-app nameOfApp

-> need reference for writing react code then download extension for react in vscode